THERE IS ONE OWNER OF ALL

24:31.625 --> 24:33.750
Don't be surprised yet!

24:34.208 --> 24:37.958
Apart from these forced wives,
Shivram Kishan also has a girlfriend.

24:38.250 --> 24:40.708
Deepika. She is very religious.

