Is this what I taught?

2:01:20.458 --> 2:01:22.458
You remember what I've always told you?

2:01:23.625 --> 2:01:27.833
Never break a woman's heart.
And never ruin a family!

2:01:29.000 --> 2:01:31.792
You broke everyone's trust.

2:01:32.917 --> 2:01:36.958
You ruined everyone's life.
Everyone's. Everyone's!

2:01:37.375 --> 2:01:40.167
Rukmani, that's enough. Stop it.

2:01:41.083 --> 2:01:46.208
I always said that my Bholu is very naive.

2:01:46.917 --> 2:01:48.083
But I was wrong.

2:01:48.917 --> 2:01:52.208
