2:01:54.083 --> 2:01:55.042
No, mother.

2:01:56.708 --> 2:01:58.333
Your Bholu is not a cheat.

2:01:59.750 --> 2:02:01.250
I have not cheated anyone.

2:02:02.958 --> 2:02:04.000
Juhi, tell me...

2:02:05.208 --> 2:02:08.875
your father placed your hand in my hand
at the hospital and passed away.

2:02:09.792 --> 2:02:13.083
Did he ever ask
whether I already had anyone in my life?

2:02:17.583 --> 2:02:18.750
And Anjali, you?

2:02:19.417 --> 2:02:23.042
You were going to commit suicide, right?
I saved your life.

2:02:23.833 --> 2:02:26.958
Your brother forced me at gunpoint
to get married to you.

2:02:28.208 --> 2:02:29.542
Who was the one who cheated?

2:02:33.875 --> 2:02:35.042
And Simran, you?

2:02:36.292 --> 2:02:41.250
I had told you that my friend fooled me
into getting married to you.

2:02:43.250 --> 2:02:44.750
But you didn't listen to me.

2:02:44.958 --> 2:02:47.667
You wanted to jump into the holy fire
and kill yourself.

2:02:48.667 --> 2:02:50.042
Should I have left you to die?

2:02:51.042 --> 2:02:55.750
If I held your hand, just to save
your life. How is that cheating?

2:02:59.250 --> 2:03:05.667
Yes, I did make one mistake, mother.
I didn't tell them about each other.

2:03:06.583 --> 2:03:09.542
Because if I had told them,
then they would have killed themselves.

2:03:10.292 --> 2:03:11.500
Now, you tell me mother,

2:03:11.917 --> 2:03:15.708
how could I kill them
after saving their lives?

2:03:18.958 --> 2:03:23.083
If there is anyone whom I have
cheated on, that is you, Deepika.

2:03:24.583 --> 2:03:27.208
I didn't tell you
that I got married thrice.

2:03:28.000 --> 2:03:29.417
Now you tell me,
what should have I done?

2:03:30.708 --> 2:03:32.292
People try to forget tragedies.

2:03:33.208 --> 2:03:35.833
But I have been living with them.

2:03:36.833 --> 2:03:38.292
I didn't want three families.

2:03:39.167 --> 2:03:41.208
But I thought
if I have been through tragedy,

2:03:41.458 --> 2:03:44.542
then they have also gone through one.
It's not their fault either.

2:03:45.167 --> 2:03:50.458
I just wanted one family.
There was just one person that I love.

2:03:51.583 --> 2:03:54.500
You, Deepu.
And I didn't want to lose you.

2:04:00.125 --> 2:04:03.292
"Never break a woman's heart.
Never ruin a family."

2:04:04.417 --> 2:04:07.292
To keep my promise to you, your Bholu,

2:04:07.375 --> 2:04:09.583
Shivram Kishan got divided
into three parts, mother.

2:04:10.750 --> 2:04:14.000
I've been running faster than a clock,
so that I can give time to everyone.

2:04:14.583 --> 2:04:15.917
I have kept everyone happy.

2:04:17.000 --> 2:04:19.458
I showed everyone my face
before I left in the morning,

2:04:19.583 --> 2:04:21.542
so that there is a smile
on their faces all day long.

2:04:24.042 --> 2:04:27.375
I tried to keep everyone happy.
Ask them, mother. Ask them.

2:04:27.667 --> 2:04:30.375
Have I not been honest in the little time
that I've spent with each of them?

2:04:30.875 --> 2:04:32.917
Have I cheated even a little?

2:04:33.750 --> 2:04:34.792
Ask them, mother.

2:04:36.250 --> 2:04:40.125
If I would've rejected them
and settled down.

2:04:40.792 --> 2:04:44.000
Then neither you nor God
would have been happy.

2:04:44.875 --> 2:04:46.958
If you still feel that I am wrong,

2:04:47.667 --> 2:04:49.875
then you can punish
me whichever way you want.

2:04:51.458 --> 2:04:52.792
You have given me life.

2:04:54.208 --> 2:05:00.458
Even if you to take that life away,
I won't say a word.

2:05:01.292 --> 2:05:02.917
Your Bholu won't say a word.

2:05:12.917 --> 2:05:14.000
Son!

2:05:28.125 --> 2:05:29.958
